Title: Department of the Southwest.
Abstract: To Major-Gen. Pleasonton: I have just returned from Cassville, and will forward my official report of the campaign in a few days. No one has fired a shot at the enemy since the battle of Newtonia, where they gained great advantage over BLUNT at first, but my command got up in time to turn the enemy's right and the tide of things.
